# QA API Testing Project

This project demonstrates basic Software Testing practices including:

- Writing test cases
- API testing
- Bug reporting
- Test documentation

The API tested in this project is a public REST API used for learning purposes.

API used:
https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com

Tools used:
- Postman
- Git
- GitHub
- VS Code

Test Coverage:
- GET /posts
- GET /users
- GET /comments

Purpose:
This project was created to demonstrate practical QA skills for a Software Testing internship.
# Test Cases

## Test Case 1

Test Case ID: TC001  
Feature: Fetch all posts  

Steps:
1. Send GET request to /posts
2. Check response status

Expected Result:
Status code should be 200  
Response should return a list of posts

