# API Testing

API Base URL:
https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com

## Endpoint 1

GET /posts

Request:
https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts

Expected Result:
- Status Code: 200
- JSON response returned
- Contains post data

---

## Endpoint 2

GET /users

Request:
https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users

Expected Result:
- Status Code: 200
- User data returned
- Each user should have ID and name

---

## Endpoint 3

GET /comments

Request:
https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/comments

Expected Result:
- Status Code: 200
- Comment data returned
# Bug Reports

## Bug Report 1

Title: API response delay

Description:
The API endpoint sometimes responds slowly.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Send GET request to /posts
2. Observe response time

Expected Result:
Response should be fast (<1 second)

Actual Result:
Response sometimes exceeds expected time

---

## Bug Report 2

Title: Missing validation on user fields

Description:
Some responses may not validate required fields.

Expected:
Each user should contain:
- id
- name
- email
Actual:
Validation not enforced